<div class="banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(-225deg, rgba(0,101,168,0.6) 0%, rgba(0,36,61,0.6) 50%), url('<%= image_path 'boxbike_banner.jpg' %>');">
  <div class="banner-content">

    <h1>Rent a Bikebox</h1>
    <p>Find the <span>perfect</span> shelter for your beloved <del>one</del> bike.</p>
    <%= link_to "See our boxes to rent", boxbikes_path %>
    <%= form_tag boxbikes_path, method: :get do %>
      <div class="search-form-control form-group">
        <%# <input class="form-control string required" type="text" name="search[query]" id="search_query" placeholder="Enter address" /> %>
        <%= text_field_tag :query,
          params[:query],
          class: "form-control string required",
          id: "search_query",
          placeholder: "Enter address"
        %>
        <%# <button name="button" type="submit" class="btn btn-flat"> %>
        <%= submit_tag "Search", class: "btn btn-primary" %>
          <%# <i class="fas fa-search mr-2"></i> Search
        </button> %>
      </div>
    <% end %>
     </div>
</div>
<div class="container" class="home-content">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div>
      <div class="align-self-center">
        <h2>Why Bikebox ?</h2>
        <p>Finding the <span style="background-color:#00b4d8; color: white">perfect</span> spot to park your bike in the city is a real pain.
        We are bike commuters like you and we decided it was time to <span style="background-color:#00b4d8; color: white">stop</span> parking our bikes in unsafe places.
        Less and less people own cars thus the number of empty boxes available grow each day, so why not use that space to park our <span style="background-color:#00b4d8; color: white">rides</span> ?</p>
      </div>
      </div>
      <div class="d-inline">
        <div class="d-flex">
          <div>
            <h2>Don't be this guy</h2>
            <p>Tired of finding your tires stabbed and flat or your seat soiled with pigeon sh*t ?
            Hate to have to check for a nice sheltered parking place to avoid rain, theft, degradation ?
            The perfect parking space is right along the corner, sign-up today to find yours.</p>
          </div>
          <%= image_tag 'bike-lamp.jpg', alt:'bike-lamp', width:'365.3px', height:'365.3px' %>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex">
          <%= image_tag 'kim.gif', alt:'kim-gif', width:'50%' %>
          <div>
            <h2>Want to make money ?</h2><br>
            <p>Bikebox lets you easily rent your box to bikers to get that sweet <span style="background-color:#00b4d8; color: white">moulaga</span>.
              Just sign-in, enter the address of the box and its details and you're ready to roll</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <br>
    <%= link_to "See our boxes to rent", boxbikes_path, class: "btn btn-flat" %>
  </div>
</div>
